<h2 class="bold font-l">Clark Griswold Freaks Out</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Clark Griswold has a few things to say about his boss after he finds out that he's not getting a Christmas bonus this year..... </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RapidFireDescriptors" class='trope-example-link'>Rapid-Fire Descriptors</a></p>
